=== center
--- wiki
&align(center){this is center aligned}
--- html
<div style="text-align:center;">this is center aligned</div>
===left
--- wiki
&align(left){this is left aligned as usual}
--- html
<div style="text-align:left;">this is left aligned as usual</div>
=== invalid value
--- wiki
&align(hoge){wrong value}
--- html
